# Set default applications to open files by extension

# Find the default application for a file extension with `duti -x<extension>`, e.g. `duti -x .txt`
# Find the bundle identifier for an application with `mdls -name kMDItemCFBundleIdentifier /Applications/<application_name>.app`, e.g. `mdls -name kMDItemCFBundleIdentifier /Applications/Visual\ Studio\ Code.app`

